from difflib import SequenceMatcher

def entrance(ss):
    max_similarity = 1
    max_pair = ()
    for i in range(len(ss)):
        x = ss[i]
        for j in range(i + 1, len(ss)):
            y = ss[j]
            s = SequenceMatcher(None, x, y)
            similarity = s.ratio()
            if similarity > max_similarity:
                max_similarity = similarity
                max_pair = (x, y)
    return max_pair
